Distribution.
E. nipponica
was known from Japan ( Tanaka & Fujita 2002 ;
Tanaka et al. 2004
) – we found it also in Kamchatka (see Fig. 1 ). The species could be present in Sakhalin Island, Kurile Islands and, Chukotka Peninsula.
